print animint

Source: R/z_print.R
print.animint.Rd

Print animint by rendering to local directory.

Usage

# S3 method for class 'animint'
print(x, ...)

Arguments

x

List of ggplots and options. In particular the out.dir option is passed along to animint2dir.

...

passed to animint2dir

Value

same as animint2dir
